AI-Powered Adaptive Traffic Management System

SmartTraffic AI is an intelligent traffic control system that uses real-time data and adaptive machine learning algorithms to optimize traffic flow, reduce congestion, and prioritize emergency vehicles. It provides live traffic visualization and dynamic signal control for smarter and safer cities.

